</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="54" pageNumber="55" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="54.[151,1437,151,501]" pageId="54" pageNumber="55">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,439,464]" pageId="54" pageNumber="55">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species name is derived from Latin 
<emphasis box="[799,885,441,464]" italics="true" pageId="54" pageNumber="55">sparsus</emphasis>
(mottled, speckled) in reference to the distinctly speckled moth (the densely irrorated thorax, tegula and forewing).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
